// Writing tests 
//    -> https://junit.org/junit5/docs/current/user-guide/#writing-tests
// Its mandatory to have test class names to follow regex pattern ^.*Tests?$. 
// It means that test class names MUST end with Test or Tests. 
// e.g. UserMgmtTests, DeviceMgmtTest etc.
//
// Running tests
// Platform = JavaUnitPlatform.class
//    -> See TestSuite class for details
//    -> https://howtodoinjava.com/junit5/junit5-test-suites-examples/#project-structure
//    -> https://junit.org/junit5/docs/current/user-guide/#running-tests
